<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Praktikum CSS</title>

<style>
*{
    box-sizing:border-box;
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
}

body{
    background-color:#add8e6;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
    padding:30px;
}

h1{
    color:white;
    font-size:40px;
    text-align:center;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    text-shadow:2px 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.description{
    background:#d3d3d3;
    color:black;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:15px;
    max-width:800px;
    margin:0 auto 30px;
    line-height:1.7;
    box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.container{
    max-width:800px;
    margin:auto;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:20px;
}

.box{
    border:2px solid black;
    padding:10px;
    height:150px;
    border-radius:15px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:bold;
    color:#333;
    box-shadow:0 5px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition:0.3s;
}

.box:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.box1{
    background:#ff9999;
}

.box2{
    background:#99ff99;
}

.box3{
    background:#9999ff;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (max-width:768px){
    .container{
        grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
    }
}

/* Smartphone */
@media (max-width:480px){
    .container{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
    }

    h1{
        font-size:28px;
    }

    .box{
        height:120px;
    }

    .description{
        padding:12px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Praktikum CSS</h1>

<p class="description">
    Selamat datang di halaman praktikum web sederhana. Halaman ini dibuat menggunakan CSS Grid dan Responsive Design. Tampilan akan menyesuaikan ukuran layar sehingga tetap rapi saat dibuka melalui komputer, tablet, maupun smartphone.
</p>

<div class="container">
    <div class="box box1">Kotak 1</div>
    <div class="box box2">Kotak 2</div>
    <div class="box box3">Kotak 3</div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
